posting_body: ['Call Now for up to $3,950 off!!!', '** -', 'show contact info', 'x 104', 'OR Text', '104', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our leasing team.', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 763 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Harborside Marina Bay Apartments in Marina del Rey, California, offers the stylish living and stunning waterfront locale you’ve been dreaming of.', 'Luxury, comfort and function are perfectly calibrated to fit your lifestyle at Harborside Marina Bay Apartments.', 'It’s a difference you’ll be able to see and feel.', 'You’ll appreciate the high-end finishes inside your home and the incredible array of community amenities at your disposal.', 'This is life on the waterfront.', 'Features:', 'Cable Ready, Whirlpool?', 'Stainless-Steel Appliances, Private Balcony or Patio, Contemporary Wood-Style & Tile Flooring, Oversized Closets, Breathtaking Marina Views*, Washer/Dryer Included, Open Floor Plans, Modern Kitchen Islands*, Quartz Countertops with Undermount Sinks, Full Height Tile Backsplashes', '*In Select Homes', 'Community Amenities:', 'Resort-Style Pool with Sundeck & Barbecue, Rooftop Lounge with Fire Pit & Barbecue, WaterBus Stop Onsite, Lush Landscaping, Marina & Boat Slips, Close to Shopping & Public Transit, Additional Onsite Storage, Bike Lockers, Business Center, WiFi Access in Common Areas, Package Acceptance Services, Resident Lounge, Easy Freeway Access, Covered Parking, State-of-the-Art Fitness Center', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets are welcome.', 'Want more info?', 'See the link below:', '<URL>', 'Prices are subject to change, based on availability and qualification of the applicant, additional fees may apply.', 'AMC-CA, Inc. dba Apartment Management Consultants-BRE #01525033', 'rKcr3Pd5']
